claim.claim-text:
1. An all-terrain riding assembly, which comprises: 
a main body member including a support surface; 
front and rear housing members supporting said main body member; 
a roller member rotatably positioned within said front housing member; 
a roller member rotatably positioned within said rear housing member; and 
means for controlling rotational velocity of said roller member positioned in said rear housing member.

4. An all-terrain riding assembly, which comprises: 
a main body member including a support surface; 
front and rear housing members supporting said main body member; 
a roller member rotatably positioned within said front housing member; 
a roller member rotatably positioned within said rear housing member; 
said rear housing member being articulatedly mounted to said main body member; and 
means for adjusting tension between said main body member and said articulatedly mounted rear housing member.
